  "title": "Amazon Linux 2022 - ALAS2022-2022-062: important priority package update for rubygem-nokogiri",
  "description": "Package updates are available for Amazon Linux 2022 that fix the following vulnerabilities:\nCVE-2022-24836:\n\tNokogiri is an open source XML and HTML library for Ruby. Nokogiri `\u003c v1.13.4` contains an inefficient regular expression that is susceptible to excessive backtracking when attempting to detect encoding in HTML documents. Users are advised to upgrade to Nokogiri `\u003e= 1.13.4`. There are no known workarounds for this issue.\n",
  "severity": "important",
